.uk%2Fthe-libertines-tickets%2Fartist%2F945319" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>提供。 </p><figure id="attachment_3809265" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3809265" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3809265" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Libertines-Gunnersbury-Park-poster.-CREDIT_-Press-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3809265" class="wp-caption-text"> Libertines Gunnersbury Park海报。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>超级草的主唱丹尼·戈菲（Danny Goffey）说：“我们很高兴与Libertines和所有其他伟大乐队一起参加当晚的Gunnersbury Park演出。</p><p> “ Gunnersbury Park是一个非常了不起的场所，可以看到乐队表演。 22年前，我们与自由主义者首次与自由主义者一起演奏，当时我们与我们一起参加了刚起步的乐队。哇...玩得开心的时候飞了。到时见！” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Libertines的谈话是干净和连接的，以“东滨海东部的安静”" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CtuPJQWz_mQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这一消息是在他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-add-more-shows-to-2024-uk-all-quiet-on-the-eastern-esplanade-tour-buy-tickets-3603175">正在进行的英国“全部安静的滨海艺术中心”之旅</a>之后，该巡回演出将在本月底结束。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-add-more-shows-to-2024-uk-all-quiet-on-the-eastern-esplanade-tour-buy-tickets-3603175">在此处</a>查看所有日期和票务信息。</p><p> Libertines的最新专辑“ All All in Eastern Eastern Esplanade”在今年早些时候发行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-libertines-all-quiet-on-the-eastern-esplanade-review-3612858"><em>NME</em>写道乐队“再次找到了他们的声音”</a> 。</p><p>四星级评论补充说：“乐队在近十年来的第一张专辑并没有与早期材料相同。他们听起来更好。”</p><p> 《东滨海滨海》中的“一切都很安静” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-reach-number-one-spot-on-album-charts-for-first-time-in-20-years-3617100">使乐队在20年来的第一张英国第一张专辑中登上了乐队</a>。在发行之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-interview-pete-doherty-carl-barat-all-quiet-eastern-esplanade-3517826">Libertines于10月与<em>NME</em>谈到了这张专辑，卡尔·巴拉特（CarlBarât）解释说，这张唱片的乐队都“面向同一方向”</a> 。</p><p> “有很多重点，每个人也一直在努力在世界上找到自己的个人地位。每个人的生活都非常不同，我们设法找到了要结合的东西。”他说。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-announce-huge-london-2025-show-at-gunnersbury-park-with-supergrass-and-more-3809236">Libertines邮报宣布，伦敦2025年在Gunnersbury Park拥有Supergrass的演出，其中更多是</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现的。</p> ;
